        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-a4d93f96-7d3e-49f8-8596-52a0cb066a55">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-a4d93f96-7d3e-49f8-8596-52a0cb066a55">
                Sir J. Grigg
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-a4d93f96-7d3e-49f8-8596-52a0cb066a55" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1944-04-04/debates/ea09e088-5f8b-4136-9a8f-d1c1f6e203c0/Demobilisation(FinancialArrangements)#contribution-a4d93f96-7d3e-49f8-8596-52a0cb066a55">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">I would refer my hon. Friend to the passage in the Prime Minister's broadcast on 26th March in which he explained that he was not in favour of disclosing our plans for demobilisation at the present time.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-a4d93f96-7d3e-49f8-8596-52a0cb066a55" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1944-04-04/debates/ea09e088-5f8b-4136-9a8f-d1c1f6e203c0/Demobilisation(FinancialArrangements)#contribution-a4d93f96-7d3e-49f8-8596-52a0cb066a55">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-12b4fcd9-6243-4245-8191-997571af865a">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-12b4fcd9-6243-4245-8191-997571af865a">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-12b4fcd9-6243-4245-8191-997571af865a">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-12b4fcd9-6243-4245-8191-997571af865a">
                Sir J. Wardlaw-Milne
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-12b4fcd9-6243-4245-8191-997571af865a" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1944-04-04/debates/ea09e088-5f8b-4136-9a8f-d1c1f6e203c0/Demobilisation(FinancialArrangements)#contribution-12b4fcd9-6243-4245-8191-997571af865a">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">While quite appreciating the point of the Prime Minister's statement, may I ask my right hon. Friend does he not think there are distinct hardships for men who are demobilised at the present time, owing to illness or disabilities which prevent them from continuing in the war? Is it not very hard on those men if no financial provision is made for them, and if they have to wait until the end of the war before they can start their ordinary occupations?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-12b4fcd9-6243-4245-8191-997571af865a" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1944-04-04/debates/ea09e088-5f8b-4136-9a8f-d1c1f6e203c0/Demobilisation(FinancialArrangements)#contribution-12b4fcd9-6243-4245-8191-997571af865a">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-8cc5b481-5953-445f-8769-4cf9144a687e">
