                Sir J. Grigg
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-8cc5b481-5953-445f-8769-4cf9144a687e" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
